<!--
Template used to generate invitation emails for students.

Parameters:
  * invitation.parent1FirstName - The first name of the first parent.
  * school.name - The name of the school which runs the MentorSuccess program.
  * programAdminName - The name of the school's program administrator.
  * programAdminEmail - The program administrator's email address.
  * programAdminPhone - The program administrator's phone number.
  * studentRegistrationUri - The URI to the registration form.
-->
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/html">
<head>
    <style>
        img {
            width: 75%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .button {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            background-color: #5DADBD;
            padding: 8px 24px 8px 24px;
            margin: 20px 20px 20px 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-top: 1px solid #CCCCCC;
            border-right: 1px solid #333333;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333333;
            border-left: 1px solid #CCCCCC;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div>
    <img src="https://mentorsuccess-public.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/email-logo.png"/>
    <p>
        Dear ${invitation.parent1FirstName},
    </p>
    <p>
        MentorSuccess™ is a K-5 student mentoring program provided through His Heart Foundation and partnered
        with ${school.name}. Focused on creating caring connections to inspire success in children, MentorSuccess™ is
        designed to enhance the social and educational experience for your child. Students and mentors work together to
        develop Leadership Success Skills involved in making life choices and creating healthy relationships for their
        future. Your child and their mentor will read books, play games and do crafts as desired. This program is
        designed to create an engaging atmosphere of healthy conversations while building stronger relationships.
    </p>
    <p>
        Program Details:
    <ul>
        <li>Mentor sessions will take place in the designated Mentor Center at ${school.name}.</li>
        <li>Mentor sessions will be supervised by ${programAdmin.name}.</li>
        <li>Parents/guardians are always encouraged and welcome to meet their student's mentor!</li>
    </ul>
    </p>
    <p>
        We thank you in advance for letting your child participate in this exciting learning experience. If you have any
        additional questions, please feel free to contact ${programAdmin.name}.<br/>
        Email: <a href="mailto:${programAdmin.email}">${programAdmin.email}</a>
        #if($programAdmin.phone)
            <br/>Phone: ${programAdmin.phone}
        #end
    </p>
    <p>
        Click the button below to register your child.<br/>
        <br/><br/>
        <a class="button" href="${studentRegistrationUri}">Register My Child</a>
        <br/><br/>
    </p>
    <p>
        <b>${programAdmin.name}</b><br/>
        MentorSuccess™ Program Administrator<br/>
        <a href="mailto:${programAdmin.email}"><b>${programAdmin.email}</b></a><br/>
        <a href="https://www.mentorsuccesskids.com">mentorsuccesskids.com</a>
    </p>
</div>
</body>
</html>